  fhir:description [ fhir:v "A sample of security labels from [Healthcare Privacy and Security Classification System](security-labels.html#hcs) that are used on events and requests/responses (aka user context or organization context) made up of PurposeOfUse and maybe a refrain/obligation."] ; # 
